<plot>Our hero's midlife crises is compounded by an unpleasant surprise - during a routine medical exam he peeks into his file and sees that he has a fatal disease and is only expected to live a few more months. Suddenly the young man's prosperous existence is turned upside down as those around him convince him to make rash decisions. When the diagnosis turns out to be a mistake, he realizes that he will never be able to make things the way they were before.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?100596</url></doc>
